p.-text
  | In this section, you can find several navigation components built with chi smaller parts. CSS has been adjusted for
  | better results in the integration of smaller navigation components.

h3 Nav Tabs
p.-text
  | You can use a combination of tabs and dropdowns for a two-level navigation menu. To accomplish with responsiveness
  | needs, you can add a <em>More</em> dropdown at the end of the menu to house the elements that overflow at the
  | end.
